cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a facial recognition tool for identifying individual macaques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The tool also involves machine learning techniques for facial recognition, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of sterilization as a population control measure, which could fall under cryptography and security (cs.CR) as well as information retrieval (cs.IR) for monitoring and tracking the population.
